metadata.description:
'i can't sleep' is our first free drop.

we made it late at night and hope u enjoy it.

more on our web 3 journey:  

in 2020 we found ourselves unable to tour for the first time since we started playing together and we began taking interest in web 3 and all the possibilities it could lead to within the music industry. 

in the beginning of 2022 we were selected as one of five artists to be part of the LNRZ freshman class and work on music nfts alongside founders Reo Cragun and clear eyes, and the rest of the freshmen (Madalen Duke, Tate Tucker, Lackhoney and Mark Jonhs).
